data.description: Luxurious 5 bedroom, 4 bath home in award-winning Rancho Sahuarita. Step inside the welcoming foyer. Flexible front room can be a formal dining room or sitting room, which flows into the butler pantry and in to the gourmet kitchen with granite counters, huge island that seats 6, double oven, breakfast nook and stainless appliances. Open floorplan great room, ideal for entertaining. Main-floor master suite with elegant double door entry, walk-in closet, deluxe master bath with dual sink exec height vanity, garden tub and separate shower. All tile floors except in Master. Deluxe laundry/craft room is loaded with cabinets and sink. Grand 8' doors thru out 1st floor. Upstairs, enjoy a large loft and gym space, 4 inviting bedrooms, and 2 full baths. Landscaped backyard w/covered patio. Only 2yrs old!
